{"tid":987558,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"工聯會:大灣區買樓陷阱多 港人慘失2000萬","createTime":"2019-01-19T11:55:08.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-19T19:36:26.000Z","uid":5195,"like":26,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"b073eba8a0cbe4cbbcef5123b53510ae3d9c4b43","tid":987558,"uid":5195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-19T11:55:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/2343144/org/d5d3fd1b20ffe6291c7dfc5ed5b8f453.JPG/a--F81fVyiGAs5z6N8i8cMsk65s8e1i56p1XFeqdVxU?v=w1280\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F2343144%2Forg%2Fd5d3fd1b20ffe6291c7dfc5ed5b8f453.JPG%2Fa--F81fVyiGAs5z6N8i8cMsk65s8e1i56p1XFeqdVxU%3Fv%3Dw1280&h=3b62a86f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n大灣區效應下，不少港人前往內地尋寶，購買各種物業作投資或出租用途。由於內地商業樓宇法例尚欠完善，且對非當地人實施限購住宅物業政策，令不少開發商有機可趁，更令不少港人「損手」。<br />\n<br />\n有港人在廣東省珠海市香洲區購入商舖，遭遇「返租」陷阱。據工聯會立法會議員何啟明透露，事件涉及300多名苦主，牽涉到大灣區9個樓盤，涉及資金約4億人民幣(約4.63億港幣)；其中有30名香港苦主，合共損失逾2,000萬人民幣（約2,314萬港幣）。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.hkcd.com/userfiles/1520470740.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkcd.com%2Fuserfiles%2F1520470740.jpg&h=8612cb00&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hkcd.com/content/2018-03/08/content_1081487.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkcd.com%2Fcontent%2F2018-03%2F08%2Fcontent_1081487.html&d=UxWdkTaPCAVmEHbvf%2Fu6KTM0pwszV1jUpWwTgNsMWwc%3D&h=22f2209b\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hkcd.com/content/2018-03/08/content_1081487.html</a><br />\n【香港商報網訊】本報兩會特派採訪組報道：工聯會四位港區全國人大代表、政協委員，包括政協委員林淑儀及黃國、人大代表吳秋北及鄭耀棠，昨日於北京會見傳媒，分享對今次人大、政協兩會的感受。他們特別強調，香港應更積極融入大灣區發展之中。"},{"pid":"d1eaaf72a54fcc6153dac90957fa889abbb72fd8","tid":987558,"uid":209773,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-19T11:55:55.000Z","msg":"工聯會？？？"},{"pid":"c7ee8a70b0a0ca57c6e613b223b10247afca903b","tid":987558,"uid":118120,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-19T11:56:52.000Z","msg